what are we doing this week?

All Integer Operations

This week, we will continue with addition and subtraction integer problems.  We will work on 1-step problems as well as multiple-step problems (Order of Operations) when negative numbers are involved.  We will move into multiplication and division as well.  Finally, we will look at how integers are used in context (that means 'in the real world').

Upcoming Assessments

WEDNESDAY:  Multiplication Facts QUIZ.  Practice 0-12 LINK

FRIDAY:  Order of Operations & Integer Operations QUIZ (includes exponents & absolute value)
